---
import Section from '../components/Section.astro';

const ideas = [
  {
    title: 'Context Is the New Prompt',
    body: 'AI cannot do a good job unless it understands the situation. The most leveraged thing you can do isn\'t writing cleverer prompts — it\'s feeding the model the right context: the document, the brief, the prior conversation, the data, the constraints, the audience.',
  },
  {
    title: 'From Copy-Paste to Connected',
    body: 'The old workflow was: copy from a doc → paste into AI → copy the answer → paste it back. The new workflow is: connect AI directly to your approved sources and tools so it can read and write where the work actually lives. Less friction, fewer errors, and the AI sees the full picture.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Cross-Model Critique',
    body: 'Use one model to challenge another. Take the output of model A, paste it into model B, and ask "what\'s wrong with this?" Different models have different blind spots; making them argue surfaces problems neither would catch alone.',
  },
  {
    title: 'AI on Your Desktop',
    body: 'AI is no longer just a browser tab. Tools like Claude for Desktop and ChatGPT\'s Mac app can read what you\'re working on, drive your applications, and stay in the flow with you. The barrier to "let me ask the AI" keeps dropping.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Agents',
    body: 'Until now: you ask, it answers, you copy-paste, you execute the plan. With agents: you ask, and it executes the plan. It books the flight, files the ticket, sends the message, runs the code. This is the next major shift, and it\'s already starting.',
  },
];
---
<Section id="beyond-prompting" number="05" title="Beyond Prompting" band="light">
  <p>
    Once you can prompt confidently, the next leap isn't a better prompt — it's changing <em>how</em> you
    work with AI. Here's where things are going.
  </p>

  <div class="beyond-list">
    {ideas.map((i, idx) => (
      <article class="beyond-row">
        <div class="beyond-num">{String(idx + 1).padStart(2, '0')}</div>
        <div class="beyond-body">
          <h3>{i.title}</h3>
          <p>{i.body}</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>

  <aside class="next-step">
    <div class="next-step-inner">
      <p class="eyebrow">Want to go deeper?</p>
      <h3>Bring AI to your team or your event</h3>
      <p>
        I work with organizations on AI strategy, implementation, and training, and give talks that make
        AI approachable for any audience. If you want help putting these ideas to work, that's where it
        happens.
      </p>
      <a class="cta-button" href="https://practicalaiservices.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        Visit practicalaiservices.com →
      </a>
    </div>
  </aside>
</Section>

<style is:global>
  .next-step {
    margin-top: 60px;
    background: var(--dark-blue);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 48px;
    color: white;
    border-left: 5px solid var(--brand-blue);
  }
  .next-step .next-step-inner { max-width: 760px; }
  .next-step .eyebrow {
    color: var(--brand-blue);
    font-size: 13px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
  }
  .next-step h3 {
    color: white;
    font-size: 30px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin: 0 0 16px 0;
  }
  .next-step p {
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0 0 24px 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .next-step { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .next-step h3 { font-size: 24px; }
  }
</style>

<style>
  .beyond-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0;
    margin: 30px 0 0 0;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.18);
  }
  .beyond-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 80px 1fr;
    gap: 24px;
    padding: 32px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 102, 204, 0.18);
    align-items: start;
  }
  .beyond-num {
    color: var(--brand-blue);
    font-weight: 800;
    font-size: 14px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    padding-top: 6px;
  }
  .beyond-body h3 {
    margin: 0 0 12px 0;
    font-size: 26px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
  }
  .beyond-body p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    margin: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .beyond-row {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 8px;
    }
    .beyond-body h3 { font-size: 22px; }
  }
</style>
